OpenHandler
The OpenHandler class is responsible for handling "Open" events in the Nonogram Maker application.

The Saveable interface defines a contract for classes that can save files.
SaveHandler
The SaveHandler class is responsible for handling "Save" events in the Nonogram Maker application.
ToggleButtonEventHandler
The ToggleButtonEventHandler class is responsible for handling events triggered by ToggleButtons in the Nonogram Maker application.
